Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.10,0:00:11.76,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\b0\fs50\1c&H4A453F&\pos(532,180)}值　日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.19,0:00:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}值日人员迟到 会给所有人添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天的菜单给你写了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:23.43,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\1c&H5F595E&\pos(440,608)}厨馀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}边角料特餐？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那太直接了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.37,0:00:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这种时候 就照平时的风格写
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.28,0:00:30.31,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\fs30\1c&H6E675F&\pos(478,110)\frz8.653\frx0\fry348}今天的菜单
