Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.28,0:00:30.31,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\b0\fs25\1c&HB4A290&\frz318.6\frx2\fry326\pos(422,442)}也要吃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}值日要说的就这些 还有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.69,0:00:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做的可尔必思是不是太淡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我还嫌浓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}穷人款可尔必思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.23,0:00:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么穷人款啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.81,0:00:46.29,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这可尔必思就是太浓才…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.57,0:00:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}负责的解释下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}唉…饮料是昨天的负责人做的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.85,0:00:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟我没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会好好处理的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.27,0:00:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.43,0:00:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人家都说风很大了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.22,0:01:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下来要做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}扫厕所！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.37,0:01:15.03,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\b0\fs35\1c&H544D46&\pos(678,206)}距离夏季队回国还有{\1c&H6C53A4&\fs55}3{\1c&H544D46&\fs35}天！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.69,0:01:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我都说过不爱吃羊栖菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别任性了 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.27,0:01:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我听说你经常贫血的 保奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.21,0:01:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又欺负人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}女高中生刚来的时候还很可爱的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.62,0:01:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人家现在又没在念书
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.72,0:01:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要喝茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太习惯南极生活 会很难回归社会的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.76,0:01:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像那样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}七条胡了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}立一发全纯三色双宝牌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉 双里宝牌就是三倍满
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:49.82,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都叫你别信筋牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我觉得那是另一种情况了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.43,0:01:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听到吸尘器的声音 就感觉在家裡似的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:01:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.23,0:02:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人家邀请我去取材了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.08,0:02:02.73,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\b0\fs30\1vc(&HD0D17C&,&HA79555&,&HD0D17C&,&HA79555&)\3c&HE6E9E6&\frz332.1\pos(760,292)}岛内散步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.08,0:02:02.73,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\b0\bord0\fs30\1c&HE1E5DC&\frz332.1\pos(660,470)}洞窟探险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.91,0:02:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在岛上散步？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.11,0:02:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.74,0:02:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和报濑昨天也被带出去散步哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.78,0:02:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么不跟我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你今天要值日嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被排挤啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.70,0:02:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}岛上散步又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.42,0:02:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我等一下要去Ice Operation呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.42,0:02:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs30\pos(745,650)}採雪任务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对喔 要抓紧时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}马上就到集合时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.42,0:02:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ice Operation是全员参加的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.99,0:02:33.93,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\b0\fs25\1vc(&HD0D17C&,&HA79555&,&HD0D17C&,&HA79555&)\3c&HE6E9E6&\pos(700,280)\frz346.9\frx340\fry2}岛内散步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.99,0:02:33.93,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\b0\bord0\fs25\1c&HE1E5DC&\frz336.7\frx358\fry4\pos(662,470)}洞窟探险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们四位将前往Ice Operation 请讲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道了 一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要搭乘哪个才好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.09,0:03:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好壮观啊 是冰山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是在凿这么大的冰山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南极禁止带出任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.34,0:03:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是唯一可以带回去留作纪念的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这裡的冰块 密封了几万年前的空气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}融化的时候会劈劈啪啪地裂开来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要不要吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是几万年前空气的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.18,0:03:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你吃得出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等我长大要拿它下酒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感觉你喝醉就会吵死人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这项工程一开始我就觉得 夏天要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很快就是秋天 又是冬天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就要过冬了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冬天都会做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很多事呢 玩游戏啊喝酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当然 做研究和观测也是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.92,0:04:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只可惜6月后 整天都会是夜晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就叫永夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有午前的地平线上 会有一丝光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.14,0:04:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一整天只会有这点变化了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其他时候就只有漫长的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直都是夜晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过也正因此 让星空美不胜收
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还能看到极光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}极光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}话说还没看过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为现在夜晚很短暂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}与企鹅拍纪念照 吃刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但极光和南极星还没看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都说了因为是永昼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但好幸福 但也好臭 但又好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:52.99,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好臭 好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回去工作了 你们好好放鬆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天是你们最后看冰海的日子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.38,0:05:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我叫你救救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不能靠近5公尺以内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想点办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们已经习惯这裡的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有这裡的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}假设啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只是假设
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反正房间空著也是空著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从这裡也能随时发影片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以也不用现在立刻回程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你肯定是要整我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会的不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}骗子！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当然要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在不回去就只能等明年了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道啊 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.70,0:06:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有信心天黑的时候能一直睡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不上学了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到时候我们回去 其他人都毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.31,0:06:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}家人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小结的电视剧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实我也有点不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你还会来这裡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哎…可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们要在这裡过冬 四个人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.64,0:06:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说好了啊 不许拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我现在很认真
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也很认真
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.78,0:06:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就好！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}话说回来 现在怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}记得队长说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最后有什么想做的 要跟她说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最后的愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样就够了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 最后我们想和这裡的人一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:23.84,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}帰り道に并んだ足音が歪んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:29.99,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}あの日之今日　违いすぎた道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:40.79,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}喉の奥に诘まるような　くすんだ视界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:44.67,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}吸い込んで吐いたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:49.81,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}いつはじまりはこのOne step
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:53.23,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}どこまでも続くこのOne step
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:58.25,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}远く远く　见たこ之ない景色へ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:04.23,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}One step One step One step
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:23.84,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}一起回家的脚步声 变得有些不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:29.99,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}今天与那天的我们 走了不一样的路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:40.79,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}景色有些暗淡 如同骨鲠在喉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:44.67,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}深吸一口气 再呼出这口气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:49.81,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}迈出这一步 就是启程的讯号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:53.23,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}迈出下一步 我们将走遍四方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:58.25,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}向远方 向远方 向陌生的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:04.23,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\3vc(&HE78928&,&HDE57B7&,&HDE57B7&,&HE78928&)}一步又一步又一步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.34,0:07:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打个好球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}藤姐加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:22.07,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拿出全力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}队长 要是我能打中 你能再考虑一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一言既出！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他还不死心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他会打中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小吟的外号可是「南极竖条纹19号」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:40.13,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※暗指坂神虎队球衣。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她投出的球是一流的 而且！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有人能躲过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放心 贵子还是打中了她投的球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.31,0:08:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}贵子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在才剪头髮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要剪就在来的时候剪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}突然想剪掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我来剪吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理 你退后点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要剪多短
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.11,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\fs60\1c&HD6B780&\rnd5\blur3\t(0,500,0\blur0)\move(396,356,396,62,0,689)}夏季队{\1c&H777271&}辛苦了{\1c&H6F3B97&}！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要磨到什么时候 人家真的要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:04.07,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\fs30\1c&H8C7668&\frx8\fry356\frz344.6\move(316,546,316,112,0,1954)}南极挑战女高中生记者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:06.88,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\fs30\1c&H8C7668&\frx8\fry356\frz344.6\move(316,112,316,-70,0,1058)}南极挑战女高中生记者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:04.78,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\1c&H8A898D&\frz331\frx18\fry342\move(514,822,514,476,0,1723)}回日本也别忘记我们喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:06.88,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\1c&H8A898D&\frz331\frx18\fry342\move(514,476,514,412,0,599)}回日本也别忘记我们喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这面旗是你们亲手做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}主宾到场啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来这裡排好队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么样 好看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们果然是母女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笑起来跟你妈一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了怎么了 她失恋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.73,0:09:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从某方面来说也没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪方面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请用想像力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}照理说我们要举行过冬交接仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但这次没有要交接的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以改为夏季队回国典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接著交给队长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所有人都辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今早天气晴朗 是个适合旅行的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本次观测之行特殊在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日本首次有女高中生观测队员参与了南极生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是次巨大的尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她们肯定都心怀不安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而我们也极度不安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但她们证明了自己是优秀的观测队员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我甚至能听到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所有男队员不希望她们回去的吵闹心声
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但她们几个要回国了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还请放弃妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最后我想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感谢大家一路的付出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等你们回国 也希望偶尔能回忆起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:11:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遥远的天边 在漆黑中默默过冬的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愿我们将来在这裡重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.17,0:11:08.71,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪粗黑\bord0\fs20\1c&H170F0C&\frz357.6\pos(316,264)\frx352\fry4}飞鸟站
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.17,0:11:08.71,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪粗黑\bord0\fs25\1c&H2A160D&\frx352\fry4\pos(312,416)\frz2.901}东京
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.17,0:11:08.71,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康俪粗黑\bord0\fs25\1c&H331B12&\frx352\fry4\frz2.901\pos(138,454)}费利曼图
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下来有请 夏季队代表的小渊泽报濑讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}各位 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想必各位都知道 我的妈妈是南极观测队员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她最喜欢的就是南极
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看著迷恋南极而离开了家的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实我对南极并没有什么好印象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想改变这种情绪 才来到了这裡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「比宇宙更远的地方」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}应该说 我的母亲是这么称呼这裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这裡 一切都毫无保留
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无论时间 生物 还是内心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这裡没有什么能保护我们 没有地方能躲藏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们的一切羞涩 与想掩盖的心事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都在这裡崭露无遗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}终于能带著眼泪 与真实的自己坦诚相见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后和大家一同跨越难关 坚持到了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}于是我才明白 妈妈爱著这裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不仅是因为景色 天空与习习凉风
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她同样爱著与伙伴一同跨越困境的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:12:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她爱的是这片不受外界影响
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:13:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}任何困难都只能和同伴一同跨越的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也爱上了这裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请努力过冬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定会回到这裡的
