Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:59.07,InSong2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3vc(&H3C50E2&,&H14D66B&,&HE29033&,&HEE6FC6&)}拿出勇气 走出大大的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是些剩的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.82,0:13:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能帮我送给 在日本等我的阿优吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.62,0:14:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你酒臭味好重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别介意 这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报濑 别忘了道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了啦 你快上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.53,0:14:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是结月的签名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很有偶像风范
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}卖掉多少张啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们别叽叽喳喳的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会期待电视剧的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然得回国再看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原来还有人在期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你得加油啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.31,0:15:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是时候出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}保重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才要向你们道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}记得一开始 我在厢型车裡说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那时候跟你们聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让我鼓起了莫大的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看著你们的脸蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就觉得这个企划绝对不能中止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原来一开始可能中止吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.89,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做大人的 该诚实的时刻就会说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}队长就麻烦你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会关心人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都上机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是不留她下来过冬 妈妈会生我的气的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就算没有这个 也不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}平均年龄马上就升上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 接下来时间就长了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:06.43,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}そっ之记した梦　言い訳ばかりして
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:17.13,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ほったらかしにしていた　叶うのが怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:25.80,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}何があるのかも　何が変わるのかも
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:31.25,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}行ってみなきゃ分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:39.16,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}さあ　一歩前に　踏み出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:45.76,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}大きな梦を叶えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:50.14,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ハ儿カ　トオクトオク
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:54.70,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真っ白な世界に　残したいな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:59.88,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}最初の足迹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:09.37,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}世界の最果てで　転がっていく太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:15.24,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}南风はやがて岛を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:19.77,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}髪を揺らす
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:31.30,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}大きな梦を叶えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:35.82,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ハ儿カ　トオクトオク
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:40.50,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}波に揺られてかた子りして
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:45.50,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}进んでいくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:49.93,InSong3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}宇宙より远くへ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:06.43,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}偷偷记下了梦想 却只找了一堆藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:17.13,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}想到自己总是忘记梦想 就怕去实现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:25.80,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}怕出什么事 怕有什么变故
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:31.25,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}但驻足不前 就什么都明白不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:39.16,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向前一步 迈出勇敢的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:45.76,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好想实现心底大大的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:50.14,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向那遥远不可及的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:54.70,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}想在那一片纯白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:59.88,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}留下我最初的脚印
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:09.37,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}红红的一轮夕阳 沉入了世界的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:15.24,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}海面南风跨越万千岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:19.77,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}吹动起我的髮梢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:31.30,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好想实现心底大大的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:35.82,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向那遥远不可及的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:40.50,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就在波涛之中举杯高歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:45.50,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}继续一步步前进
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:49.93,InSong3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}去比宇宙更遥远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:07.55,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康粗圆体\bord0\fs25\1c&H3E456F&\be1\frx22\fry344\frz346\move(130.8,444,153.6,404,36,2706)}寄件备份
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚来的时候还觉得好远的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}旅行就是这样子的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这还不是结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有60度 50度 40度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咆哮！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定又要吐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算再吐几次 再觉得难受得想死 也没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无所谓 这也是旅行的一环
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不觉得我们变坚强了点？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也可能是变随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为这裡的一切都很大嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要穿成这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最后的机会了 当然要把这身穿整齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我看一下 亮眼睿智激…激动人心的报导也是最后的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.25,0:18:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我看还是别用稿子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}淮备 要拍萝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要开拍了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再等等 还差一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是极光
